      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under the same 5 flow-speed operating points as the COU. Fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C, 40% hematocrit) match COU conditions. Validation relevance meets Gradation 2."
    },
