      "rationale": "Model form assessment not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The k-omega SST turbulence model with power-law hemolysis model is standard practice for centrifugal blood pump CFD; formal model form uncertainty analysis deferred to higher MRL."
